com.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.strategy

Class ReadOnlyGraphStrategy

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.strategy.ReadOnlyGraphStrategy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GraphStrategy

    public class ReadOnlyGraphStrategy
extends Object
implements GraphStrategy
    This GraphStrategy prevents the graph from being modified and will throw a UnsupportedOperationException if an attempt is made to do so.
    Author:
    Stephen Mallette (http://stephen.genoprime.com)
